urlLink USA-Presidents.Info - Biographies and information on every American president.  This is a nice site that I am sure will serve as a primary reference tool for many children doing homework.  It is a straight forward site which has biographies (with pictures) of American presidents.  There are no stupid banner ads slowing the site down.  It also is integrating data from Wikipedia.  A couple of famous presidents;   urlLink George Washington   urlLink Thomas Jefferson   urlLink Abraham Lincoln   urlLink FDR   urlLink John F. Kennedy   urlLink Ronald Reagan   urlLink George Herbert Walker Bush   urlLink Bill Clinton   urlLink George W. Bush